        <h3>Dubai Courts to DIFC</h3>

        <p>A Dubai Courts judgment being recognized by DIFC Courts needs certified English translation. Arabic evidence and supporting documents must be translated for the DIFC registry to process the matter.</p>

        <h3>Planning for Both Systems</h3>

